node.title: Matildas seek revenge against world champions USA in Sydney
node.alt: Alex Morgan dribbles towards Sam Kerr.
node.description: The Matildas welcome world champions USA on home soil for the first time in 21 years. Follow our live-blog for all action.
node.content: ["It's been over two decades since the number one-ranked USA played on Australian shores.", "Since then, Australia and the US have faced each other 31 times, with the Matildas winning just once \u2014\u00a0a 1-0 victory at the 2017 Tournament of Nations.", "Can Australia, led by the red-hot Sam Kerr, exact their revenge on their old foes? Or will the Americans\u00a0re-assert their dominance over the plucky underdogs?", "Follow all the action live below."]
